data.description: Welcome to your dream home in a prestigious gated private subdivision! This exquisite custom-built residence boasts luxury at every turn. Step inside to discover a spacious, sunlit living space adorned with quartz countertops, complemented by elegant tile and wood laminate floors that create a warm, inviting atmosphere.    The heart of this home is the stunning gourmet kitchen, perfect for culinary enthusiasts and entertaining guests. Outside, indulge in relaxation in your lavish pool, surrounded by a meticulously landscaped backyard that offers ample space for all to play freely.    Upstairs, a dedicated teen suite provides privacy and independence for anyone, making this home ideal for families of all sizes. Plus, there's a convenient storage building for all your organizational needs.    Don't miss the opportunity to call this extraordinary property yours. Experience the epitome of luxury living – schedule your private tour today!
